word_mean_info__list.difference: 为正式用词，表由于组成部分太多，相互关系太复杂而不能理解，语气很强。
侧重内在关系的复杂，需通过仔细研究与了解才能掌握和运用。
与complex的含义接近，但语气更强，着重极其复杂，很难分析、分辨或解释。
侧重指事物发展到或达到高级的程度所体现出的复杂。
着重指错综复杂，令人迷惑理解。

list.abstract: complex（英[ˈkɒmpleks]，美[kəmˈpleks , ˈkɑːmpleks]），英语单词，作形容词用，为由许多部分组成的；组合的；合成的。作名词用，为建筑群；服务设施集中区；情结。作动词用，为使络合；形成综合体；组成复合体。短语搭配有superiority complex（自大情结），例句为“Plant biology is complex and fascinating.（植物生物学是复杂而迷人的）”。 complex形容词类近义词有sophisticated、involved、synthetic等，相关反义词有simple，名词为complexity，比较级为more complex。

yingyinNormal.en: A highly complex computational system hiding in plain sight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个极度复杂的电脑系统隐于闹市之中。

yingyinNormal.en: All of this is one little girl's bedroom, every moment. It's infinitely complex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 全部的这些，都在这一个小女孩的卧室，每一个时刻，这是极其复杂的。

yingyinNormal.en: So, here's the rub. Somehow, we have to have complex astrophysical engineering conversations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么，问题就是有时候,，我们总要进行复杂的天体物理工程学交流。

yingyinNormal.en: To keep the power on, we rely on what's been called the largest and most complex machine in the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要保持供电，我们依赖一种大而复杂的机器。

yingyinNormal.en: We converted the data produced by those sensors, revealing stunningly complex wind patterns sped up 10,000 times.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们传递这些传感器产生的数据，揭示极其复杂的风模式这加速了10000倍。

yingyinNormal.en: You've dedicated your life's work to educating the general populace about complex scientific ideas. Yes, in part.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您一直致力于向公众宣传灌输一些复杂的科学理念。对，差不多。

yingyinNormal.en: Repair workers like Ryan and Vinnie are on the front lines every day, maintaining the grid's complex delivery system.
yingyinNormal.zh: 像赖安和维尼这样的修理工，每天都奋斗在前线，保养复杂的输电网系统。

yingyinNormal.en: I am a smart man. A genius. Yes, and I've created something so complex, I can't positively tell what it can do and what it can't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是个聪明人。是个天才。的确，我创造了一个复杂的东西，我无法确定它能干什么，不能干什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Enter the Federal Aviation Administration, or FAA, which maintains our complex flight-management system today. Here's how it works.
yingyinNormal.zh: 进入联邦导航系统，它包括了我们现代复杂的航空管理系统，则是它的运作方式。

yingyinNormal.en: But it's actually your brain running a complex series of calculations within a matter of seconds that's responsible for determining attraction.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但其实那是你的脑袋在数秒之间处理一连串复杂的计算，最后决定了什么对你有吸引力。

yingyinNormal.en: In other words, the brain seems to be tracking low-level, statistical properties of behavior in order to make complex decisions regarding other people's character.
yingyinNormal.zh: 换言之，大脑似乎会根据统计中较低机率的行为特征针对他人的个性做出复杂的决定。

yingyinNormal.en: Mine it? Like, mining gold? Sort of. There's a limited amount, and we find it, not by tunneling into the earth, but by using a computer to solve complex mathematical problems.
yingyinNormal.zh: 挖？就像挖金子吗？类似吧。比特币的总数是有限的，我们想获得，不是往地心挖坑，而是用电脑运算复杂的数学问题来获得。

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard, you will be doing a series of complex mathematical problems on a vintage Casio model 1175 calculator watch I received when I won the Earth Science medal in 3rd grade. Treat it with respect.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱纳德，你要处理一系列复杂的数学问题，使用我在3年级时勇夺地球科学金牌时获得的老式卡西欧1175型计算器手表，要好好待它。

yingyinNormal.en: If a potential mate has managed to pass all these tests, there's still one more: the infamous first kiss, a rich and complex exchange of tactile and chemical cues, such as the smell of one's breath, and the taste of their mouth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果有某个可能的对象通过这些检验，最后还有一项：恶名昭彰的初吻，初吻交换丰富而复杂的触觉及化学信号，像是呼吸的气味及嘴巴的味道。

yingyinNormal.en: She and her colleagues gently extract you from the surrounding sediment, measure and photograph all the bits and pieces they find, and begin the complex task of reconstructing how and when you lived based on the evidence they find in your bones.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她和她的同事们小心翼翼地把你从周围沉积物中取出，测量、拍照对他们发现的一点一滴，然后基于他们在你骨骼中发现的证据开始复杂的工作，重现你如何以及何时生活过。

yingyinNormal.en: No. Stan here is much more complex than that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，对于这位斯坦原因要复杂多了。

yingyinNormal.en: My guess is former military with a side of hero complex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我猜你是退役军人，有点英雄情结。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, but some people have that complex, don't they? An idee fixe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，但有些人就是有这种情结，对吧？固定观念[法语]。

yingyinNormal.en: The apartment complex that blew up, Petrov used that to justify invading Chechnya.
yingyinNormal.zh: 公寓被炸事件成了佩特罗夫用来进攻车臣的理由。

yingyinNormal.en: To understand what's happening, you need to enter a complex and microscopic world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要想弄明白光合作用原理，我们需要进入一个显微镜下的复杂世界。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: consisting of many different and connected parts

examination_example.sentence: A moralist, satirist, and social reformer, Dickens crafted <highlight>complex</highlight> plots and striking characters that capture the panorama of English society.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为一名道德家、讽刺作家和社会改革家，狄更斯精心设计了复杂的情节和引人注目的人物，捕捉了英国社会的全貌。

examination_example.sentence: In Cambodia, the choice of a spouse is a <highlight>complex</highlight> one for the young male.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在柬埔寨，对年轻男性来说，择偶是一件复杂的事情。

examination_example.sentence: It takes a while to judge <highlight>complex</highlight> aspects of personality, like neuroticism or open-mindedness.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 判断性格的复杂方面，比如神经质或思想开放，需要一段时间。

sense_info_list.en: a group of similar buildings or facilities on the same site

examination_example.sentence: The researchers mapped not only the city's vast and ornate ceremonial areas, but also hundreds of simpler apartment <highlight>complexes</highlight> where common people lived.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员不仅绘制了这座城市巨大而华丽的礼仪区，还绘制了数百个普通人居住的简单公寓建筑群。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 含义中有"多种因素交错在一起"这一层意思，从而可能显得非常复杂。侧重内在关系的复杂，需通过仔细研究与了解才能掌握和运用。
为正式用词，表由于组成部分太多，与 complex 的含义接近，但语气更强，着重极其复杂，很难分析、分辨或解释。
着重指错综复杂，令人迷惑理解。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The main cutting tools aren't <highlight>complex</highlight>(复杂的): paper and scissors or a knife, but clever and skilled paper-cutting artists.

examination_example.sentence: "The <highlight>complex</highlight> (复杂的) steps make it hard to hand down the folk art," she said.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她说：“复杂的步骤使得民间艺术难以传承。”

examination_example.sentence: They help the bus to deal with <highlight>complex</highlight> (复杂的) road conditions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们帮公交车处理复杂的路况。
